PrecisAuthority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the Province of ONTARIO and THE PERLEY HOSPITAL which provides for the transfer to the Province and subsequently to the hospital of the lands, premises, equipment and furnishings associated with the RIDEAU VETERANS' HOME, 363 Symth Road, Ottawa, Ontario, both of whom undertake to construct and operate a community hospital for veterans on those grounds.
